'''加利·安德魯·史必'''{{MBE}}<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/wales/8735700.stm |title=Speed leads Welsh sport honours |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-06-11 |accessdate=2010-06-12 |archive-date=2010-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100613072849/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/wales/8735700.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|'''Gary Andrew Speed'''}}，{{bd|1969年|9月8日|2011年|11月27日|Speed, Gary}}<ref name="rte"/>）是一位[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]前[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，於球員末期效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]兼任[[教練|教練]]，退役後出任領隊，2010年至2011年11月曾執教[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國家隊]]，任內自殺逝世。

==生平==
===球員===
史必於1988年加盟[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]開始球員生涯，1992年協助球會奪得甲組聯賽冠軍，翌年參加首屆[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英超]]，1996年轉投另一間英超球會[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]，1998年以550萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉會至[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]，當時獲領隊[[博比·罗布森|博比·罗布森]]賞識，多年來一直長期擔任[[中場|中場]]正選位置，效力7年間一共替球會上陣超過200場聯賽。

2004年，35歲的史必離開紐卡素以75萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]身價加盟球員生涯第四間[[英超|英超]]球會[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，2006年12月9日，史必協助保頓4-0擊敗[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，並且慶祝成為第一位上陣[[英超|英超]]累積達第500場的球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6167279.stm |title=Shearer lauds record-making Speed |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-11 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202233945/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6167279.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；2007年8月25日，史必在對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]時頭球頂入，成為當時[[英超|英超]]成立以來能夠在所有賽季取得入球唯一的球員，稍後史必的[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾士]]隊友，效力[[曼聯|曼聯]]的[[瑞恩·吉格斯|傑斯]]亦成功造到，並將紀錄一直伸延至2010/11年球季仍未中斷。

2007年5月1日，[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]領隊[[萨姆·阿勒代斯|艾拿戴斯]]意外地離隊後，史必獲新任領隊[[森美·李爾|森美·李爾]]委派擔任一隊教練<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6610581.stm |title=Speed handed Bolton coaching role |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-01 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2007-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027084352/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6610581.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，惟於同年10月辭任專注於球員崗位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/7039158.stm |title=Speed steps down as Bolton coach |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-11 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2012-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202232221/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/7039158.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。史必曾保持[[英超|英超]]最多上陣紀錄，1992年效力列斯聯時在8月15日對[[溫布頓足球會|溫布頓]]首次[[英超|英超]]上陣開始，直到2007年年底離開保頓加盟[[英冠|英冠]]的[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，史必累積上陣535場，直到年前才被[[大卫·詹姆斯|大卫·詹姆斯]]打破。

2007年12月28日，史必以先借後買的形式轉投[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，轉會費約25萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7158844.stm |title=Blades complete Speed loan deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-02 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2008-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225222516/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7158844.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，首場賽事是2008年1月1日對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的賽事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7163905.stm |title=Wolves 0-0 Sheff Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-01 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2008-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104060706/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7163905.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，同年3月對[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]的賽事中攻入首個加盟後的入球，當時主射[[十二碼|十二碼]]為對方門將撲出後補中<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7285092.stm |title=Sheff Utd 2-1 Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-11 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2011-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130013732/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7285092.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。史必一直擔任錫菲聯的常規正選，雖然其合約包含轉任教練的條款，他表示沒有退役的計劃<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7324340.stm |title=Speed wants to carry on playing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-01 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224090433/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7324340.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而時任領隊[[凯文·布兰克威尔|布兰克威尔]]（Kevin Blackwell）於2008/09年球季委任史必成為球員兼教練<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7330665.stm |title=Speed set for more responsibility |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-04 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2009-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108003757/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7330665.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但到季中史必受到背傷困擾，需要接受[[手術|手術]]治療而缺席球季餘下賽事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/blades/Speed-career-under-threat.4808408.jp |title=Speed career under threat |publisher=thestar.co.uk |date=2008-12-19 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090309113627/http://www.thestar.co.uk/blades/Speed-career-under-threat.4808408.jp |archive-date=2009-03-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>，史必轉心於教練工作。

2010年8月11日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]錫菲聯作客出戰[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:哈特尔普尔; zh-hk:哈特普爾;}-]]，已有年多沒有上陣的史必擔任沒有上陣的後補球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8901030.stm |title=Hartlepool 2-0 Sheff Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-11 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2010-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819052017/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8901030.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===領隊===
2010年夏季[[保罗·索萨|保罗·索萨]]與[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]提前解約後，史雲斯要求錫菲聯准許與史必商討加盟條件被拒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8797974.stm |title=Blades reject Swansea City's approach for Gary Speed |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-09 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2010-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100804060239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8797974.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。而已考獲[[欧足联职业教练证书|欧足联职业教练证书]]（UEFA Pro Licence）的史必表明希望擔任領隊之職，而錫菲聯已視他為布兰克威尔的繼任人選<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8891453.stm |title=Gary Speed reveals managerial ambition |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-06 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2010-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819071900/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8891453.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。當錫菲聯於2010/11年球季開季成績未如理想，球隊與布兰克威尔協議提前解約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8914869.stm |title=Kevin Blackwell leaves Sheffield Utd by mutual consent |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-14 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2010-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818061359/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8914869.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於2010年8月17日正式委任史必出任新領隊，簽約三年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8918047.stm |title=Sheffield United announce Gary Speed as new manager |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-17 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2010-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818173549/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8918047.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

錫菲聯在史必麾下表現不振，帶領18場輸掉一半賽事，球隊在聯賽榜僅比降班區域高兩位及差1分，但於出任僅四個月後，於2010年12月14日獲[[威爾斯足球總會|威爾斯足球總會]]聘任為[[威爾斯足球代表隊|國家隊]]第11任領隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/9274410.stm |title=Wales unveil ex-captain Gary Speed as new manager |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-14 |accessdate=2010-12-15 |archive-date=2010-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101215045706/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/9274410.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
史必曾經擔任[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾士]]隊長，並且代表過[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾士]]上陣85場國際賽，2004年舉行的[[2006年世界盃足球賽|世界盃]]外圍賽中，[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾士]]以3-2擊敗[[波蘭國家足球隊|波蘭]]後，當時是球隊[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]的史必宣佈退出國家隊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/3741366.stm |title=Speed retires from Wales |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-10-13 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2017-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212023057/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/3741366.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，是目前（2010年8月）[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾士]]上陣次數第二高的球員，僅次於[[内维尔·索夏尔|修禾路]]（Neville Southall）的92次最多紀錄。

==自杀==
2011年11月27日，威爾士足總發表聲明，指史必去世，終年42歲<ref>[http://rthk.hk/rthk/news/expressnews/news.htm?expressnews&20111127&55&801013 威爾士領隊史必去世 終年42歲]</ref>。[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]和[[英国独立新闻公司|英国独立新闻公司]]报导称他是在位于英格兰[[柴郡|柴郡]]亨廷顿的家中上吊自杀<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite web|last=Hughes|first=Mark|title=Wales boss Gary Speed found dead|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/8918628/Wales-boss-Gary-Speed-found-dead.html|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=27 November 2011|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822065329/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/8918628/Wales-manager-Gary-Speed-found-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ITN>{{cite web|title=Gary Speed found hanged at home|url=http://www.itn.co.uk/sport/34190/Gary+Speed+dies|work=ITN|accessdate=27 November 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111129160647/http://www.itn.co.uk/sport/34190/Gary%20Speed%20dies|archivedate=2011年11月29日}}</ref>。柴郡警察局发表声明称斯皮德的死亡并没有疑点<ref name=ESPN>{{cite web|author=ESPNsoccernet staff|title=Gary Speed dies aged 42|url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/989128/wales-boss-gary-speed-dies-aged-42?cc=5739|work=ESPN Soccernet|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=27 November 2011|archive-date=2011-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130022420/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/989128/wales-boss-gary-speed-dies-aged-42?cc=5739|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而斯皮德的死亡则让他的朋友感到震惊，在他死亡前几个小时，他还在[[英国广播公司第一台|BBC一台]]足球节目《足球焦点》中以嘉宾的身份录制节目<ref>{{cite news|title=Shock as Wales football manager Gary Speed dies at 42|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-15911321|accessdate=27 November 2011|newspaper=BBC News|date=27 November 2011|archive-date=2011-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128104827/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-15911321|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

